data.description: Welcome to this fully beautiful, high-end remodeled solar home within the Great Oak High boundary at the community of Temecula Creek. Located in the end of Cul-de-sac and oriented North-South. Open concept and High Ceiling catch your eyes at the first sight. The property features 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, 3-car garage. Offers one main Floor bedroom and laundry room downstairs. All the floorings upgraded and crown moldings throughout the house. All exquisite quality countertops, showers, bathtubs, cabinets throughout. Gourmet kitchen, you share a wonderful time with family here. Upstairs spacious loft and has 3 remaining bedrooms. Low maintenance backyard and mature sweet fruit trees planted, you will be excitedly looking forward to lemon, fig and orange at the harvest season. The community near the park and trail, Temecula wine country just 1 mile away. Near everything you can mention. Great Location.
